          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1113.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>sliced spring greens </strong>to the reserved pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook them for 3-4 min or until they're tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1113.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1113.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
