            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Pat your<strong> cod fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Once the pan is hot, add the <strong>cod</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it's opaque and flakes easily</p>",
